{"tid":1591200,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【鄺俊宇遇襲】民主黨：全程有人攝錄有預謀 質疑涉及買兇","createTime":"2019-09-24T05:08:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T05:09:53.000Z","uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3a225693bdec0c244d4e64e19432087a220e30e6","tid":1591200,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:08:54.000Z","msg":"民主黨林卓廷表示，立法會議員鄺俊宇今早10時許，在天水圍濕地公園一個停車場，被3人襲擊受傷，送往天水圍醫院救治。他說，鄺俊宇被人拳打腳踢，後頸受傷。對於鄺俊宇被襲，民主派感憤怒，並予以強烈譴責。<br />\n<br />\n民主派指，有人在襲擊期間拍片，拍攝整個襲擊過程，是不尋常的做法，明顯是有預謀，質疑是否買兇，錄影是要向某人交代。民主派指，今次不是單一事件，民主黨辦事處過去一段時間多次受到破壞，懷疑當中背後有人策劃，質疑襲擊的人有黑社會背景人士，又認為，明顯是針對反修例運動組織人士，圖施襲以暴力圖令他們「收聲」退縮，強調不會受暴力威嚇，會堅持五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n他們希望市民如果見到施襲過程，向他們提供線索，向警方施壓下，令他們認真處理和跟進此事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1098065/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E9%84%BA%E4%BF%8A%E5%AE%87%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%BB%A8-%E5%85%A8%E7%A8%8B%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E6%94%9D%E9%8C%84%E6%9C%89%E9%A0%90%E8%AC%80-%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E8%B2%B7%E5%85%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1098065%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E9%2584%25BA%25E4%25BF%258A%25E5%25AE%2587%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25A5%25B2-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E9%25BB%25A8-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%25A8%258B%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2594%259D%25E9%258C%2584%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%25A0%2590%25E8%25AC%2580-%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%258F%258A%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E5%2585%2587&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=7cf1e5ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1098065%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E9%2584%25BA%25E4%25BF%258A%25E5%25AE%2587%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25A5%25B2-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E9%25BB%25A8-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%25A8%258B%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2594%259D%25E9%258C%2584%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%25A0%2590%25E8%25AC%2580-%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%258F%258A%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E5%2585%2587&h=2a5862d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1098065/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E9%84%BA%E4%BF%8A%E5%AE%87%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%BB%A8-%E5%85%A8%E7%A8%8B%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E6%94%9D%E9%8C%84%E6%9C%89%E9%A0%90%E8%AC%80-%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E8%B2%B7%E5%85%87</a>"},{"pid":"dde68ffb047a00e95779401b3a44ee5802955c02","tid":1591200,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:09:53.000Z","msg":"淋病話會公正處理喎"}]}